title: Redfish Environment Metrics
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors aggregate environment metrics of Redfish devices that
 use the newer Sensor resource model. It reports system power consumption
 and, if available, fan speeds and temperatures as performance data.

discovery:
 One service is created for each chassis environment metrics resource.

item:
 The ID of the environment metrics resource.
